---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Acerca de Lumina Consulting - Nuestra Misión y Visión"
  description="Conoce nuestra misión de iluminar el camino hacia la eficiencia empresarial transformando datos en información estratégica."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-24 bg-lumina-navy overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 -right-32 w-96 h-96 bg-lumina-blue/15 rounded-full blur-3xl" />
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 -left-32 w-96 h-96 bg-lumina-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl" />
    </div>
    <div class="container-custom relative">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <span class="badge bg-white/10 text-white border-white/20 mb-6">Nosotros</span>
        <h1 class="text-white mb-6">Acerca de Lumina Consulting</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-lumina-slate-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Iluminando el camino hacia la eficiencia empresarial
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- Mission -->
          <div class="card text-center scroll-fade">
            <div class="icon-container icon-container-lg mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4">Nuestra Misión</h2>
            <p class="text-lumina-slate">
              Iluminar el camino hacia la eficiencia empresarial, transformando datos dispersos en información estratégica que impulse el crecimiento y la toma de decisiones inteligentes.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Vision -->
          <div class="card text-center scroll-fade animation-delay-100">
            <div class="icon-container icon-container-lg mx-auto mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-lumina-accent/10 to-lumina-blue/10">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-lumina-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.519 4.674a1 1 0 00.95.69h4.915c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-3.976 2.888a1 1 0 00-.363 1.118l1.518 4.674c.3.922-.755 1.688-1.538 1.118l-3.976-2.888a1 1 0 00-1.176 0l-3.976 2.888c-.783.57-1.838-.197-1.538-1.118l1.518-4.674a1 1 0 00-.363-1.118l-3.976-2.888c-.784-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h4.914a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.519-4.674z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4">Nuestra Visión</h2>
            <p class="text-lumina-slate">
              Ser el faro que guíe a PyMEs y startups hacia la automatización inteligente y el análisis de datos estratégico, liberando su potencial de crecimiento.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach -->
  <section class="py-24 section-light">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-fade">
        <span class="badge mb-4">Filosofía</span>
        <h2>Nuestro Enfoque</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="feature-card scroll-fade">
          <div class="icon-container mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg mb-3">Lean y Eficiente</h3>
          <p class="text-lumina-slate text-sm">
            Creemos en soluciones prácticas que generen valor inmediato sin burocracia innecesaria.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card scroll-fade animation-delay-100">
          <div class="icon-container mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg mb-3">Tecnología con Propósito</h3>
          <p class="text-lumina-slate text-sm">
            Utilizamos herramientas avanzadas (Python, Power BI, IA) para resolver problemas reales de negocio.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-card scroll-fade animation-delay-200">
          <div class="icon-container mb-5">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg mb-3">Resultados Medibles</h3>
          <p class="text-lumina-slate text-sm">
            Cada proyecto se enfoca en generar impacto cuantificable en la operación de nuestros clientes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Methodology -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-fade">
        <span class="badge mb-4">Proceso</span>
        <h2>Nuestra Metodología</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-6 scroll-fade">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-lumina-blue to-lumina-accent text-white flex items-center justify-center font-display font-bold text-xl">
              1
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Diagnóstico</h3>
              <p class="text-lumina-slate">
                Identificamos procesos ineficientes y oportunidades de automatización
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6 scroll-fade animation-delay-100">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-lumina-blue to-lumina-accent text-white flex items-center justify-center font-display font-bold text-xl">
              2
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Diseño</h3>
              <p class="text-lumina-slate">
                Creamos soluciones a medida que se integren naturalmente con la operación
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6 scroll-fade animation-delay-200">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-lumina-blue to-lumina-accent text-white flex items-center justify-center font-display font-bold text-xl">
              3
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Implementación</h3>
              <p class="text-lumina-slate">
                Desarrollamos e implementamos las soluciones con mínima disrupción
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6 scroll-fade animation-delay-300">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-lumina-blue to-lumina-accent text-white flex items-center justify-center font-display font-bold text-xl">
              4
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Capacitación</h3>
              <p class="text-lumina-slate">
                Transferimos conocimiento para que el equipo pueda mantener y evolucionar las soluciones
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex gap-6 scroll-fade animation-delay-400">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-lumina-blue to-lumina-accent text-white flex items-center justify-center font-display font-bold text-xl">
              5
            </div>
            <div class="pt-2">
              <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Seguimiento</h3>
              <p class="text-lumina-slate">
                Monitoreamos resultados y optimizamos continuamente
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="py-24 section-light">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-fade">
        <span class="badge mb-4">Diferenciadores</span>
        <h2>¿Por qué elegir Lumina Consulting?</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card scroll-fade">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lumina-success/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lumina-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Experiencia Comprobada</h3>
              <p class="text-lumina-slate text-sm">Casos de éxito en diferentes industrias</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-100">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lumina-success/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lumina-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Enfoque Integral</h3>
              <p class="text-lumina-slate text-sm">Combinamos análisis de negocio con implementación técnica</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-200">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lumina-success/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lumina-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Soporte Continuo</h3>
              <p class="text-lumina-slate text-sm">Acompañamos el proceso de adopción y optimización</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card scroll-fade animation-delay-300">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-lumina-success/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-lumina-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg mb-2">Escalabilidad</h3>
              <p class="text-lumina-slate text-sm">Soluciones que crecen con tu negocio</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-lumina-navy relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-lumina-blue/10 rounded-full blur-3xl" />
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-lumina-accent/10 rounded-full blur-3xl" />
    </div>
    <div class="container-custom relative">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-white mb-6 scroll-fade">¿Listo para comenzar?</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-lumina-slate-light mb-10 scroll-fade animation-delay-100">
          Conversemos sobre cómo podemos ayudar a tu empresa
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/56991629095?text=Hola,%20me%20interesa%20conocer%20más%20sobre%20Lumina%20Consulting"
          target="_blank"
          class="btn-primary scroll-fade animation-delay-200"
        >
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/>
          </svg>
          Contactar por WhatsApp
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
